<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٨٢٤ - حَدَّثَنَا عَبْدُ اللَّهِ بْنُ مَسْلَمَةَ، عَنْ مَالِكٍ، عَنْ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ دِينَارٍ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ ابْنِ عُمَرَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">أَنَّ رَسُولَ اللَّهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">(إِنَّ الْغَادِرَ يُنْصَبُ لَهُ لِوَاءٌ يَوْمَ الْقِيَامَةِ،<span class="c5"> فَيُقَالُ:</span> هَذِهِ غَدْرَةُ فُلَانِ بْنِ فُلَانٍ)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[ر: ٣٠١٦]</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>